snippet.title: Gears 5 - Official Campaign Story Trailer | Gamescom 2019
snippet.description:
With all-out war descending, Kait Diaz breaks away to uncover her connection to the enemy and discovers the true danger to Sera – herself.

#Gears5 launches on September 10th. Play 4 days early with Xbox Game Pass Ultimate or the Gears 5: Ultimate Edition.
